{"tid":1365880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.27之前，入嚟一齊度掂佢，上環依單手尾長，隨時引爆","createTime":"2019-07-25T19:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T19:29:48.000Z","uid":287132,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b46b64b8eb349905cf0257eeee286d288bf37c04","tid":1365880,"uid":287132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:18:42.000Z","msg":"原居民一件，對大眾嚟講元朗事件好大，對我更加大啦。如果大家跟得貼，都知國家輿論機器在何君堯領導下，開始染指鄉事勢力範圍，依個星期頻頻發放Whatsapp吹風放好多假新聞，所以我一直都忙於做中間人，拆解依家有這個狀態。劉後主今日講明有人放假消息激化矛盾，亦都證明我推論無錯。<br />\n<br />\n主戰場固然離唔開「大肚婆」「林卓廷先撩者賤」「飛天南有無比人掟磚」「燒村拆祠堂」同埋悶到抽筋既外國勢力論，對任何人嚟講都好易拆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但芸芸訊息之中，即使7.21當晚我在港島發夢，我都從來唔知發生過，後知後覺咗：就係<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">貨van司機事件</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n依單嘢睇好似可以冷處理，但串連埋屯元天公海有人被cap圖要去雞地拆車，加上何妖祖墳被扑，已經令唔單止鄉紳，連一般唔理事的鄉豬都極為敏感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於當晚戰線拉得好長，義士一時唔為意中間trap咗啲車好合理，但路過的司機未必會理解，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">保持克制</span></strong>理解包容，用放行比十字車一樣的心態，令人覺得示威者重視佢搵食既意願，互相尊重先可以爭取到支持同體諒（唔確認係仆街藍絲之前都要保持質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<br />\n<br />\n搵食依點其實同班鄉事好似，佢地都只係想繼續響元朗fing同埋happy，先至有今日自衛同埋守村界既呼籲。<br />\n<br />\n翻嚟正題，睇翻東方事主受訪講法，以及朋友在連登對事主的形容，<br />\n<br />\n我認識藍色貨van 司機，有啲野想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356240</a><br />\n<br />\n所謂橋唔怕舊，最緊要受，最簡單：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用翻稅務大樓道歉果招</span></strong></span> ，不過搵個代理做，未諗到搵邊個好。<br />\n<br />\n記住佢就算再港豬，都經朋友認咗衰仔。大家何必少一個支持之餘，仲要留咁大壇拆唔到既武器比建制無限loop？最緊要既，係佢真係無撐政府，行事唔可以完全失去正當性，不然連手足都會開始互相懷疑。至於財物損失，要諗清楚點做，唔好比人錯覺抗支金係用嚟做賠償而壯膽去扑更多野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一點我最想一齊諗一齊做好既，就係點樣去用好大家既<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">肢體語言</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n戰場上面瞬息萬變，除非fact checking十級重要之外，肢體語言亦都係唔可以睇輕。雖然發得夢多既手足一定識手語，對人去遮鏡頭的動作都有默契，會容許到有啲侵略性既動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">不過一般市民根本唔知大家做緊乜</span></strong>，當晚最唔理想就係在玻璃前高舉雪糕筒，發夢見到遮車cam，現實以為扑玻璃，真係差好遠。做每個動作前，諗清楚，諗清楚，諗清楚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人唔算超級和理非，但如果元朗萬一真係發生同類型不必要衝突，兩件事加埋會成為文宣組點都無得拆的perfect storm。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我已經決定咗當日會第一次上前排，在村民同衝衝子之間做調停，想像唔到當日大家會用咩方法，一定要克制啊，無NONO無衡突我們仲威啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90d2f1aac3c4f976c4db769e0da93592cdbae1e","tid":1365880,"uid":287132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:21:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16051d956e0e29a2de843d94c0253dce19ee9fda","tid":1365880,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:21:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推 <br />\n<br />\n無謂的敵人就唔建立<br />\n<br />\n但邊個鄉黑衝出黎搞事我地一定同你搞到底</span>"},{"pid":"0a53bb4389f12a8bb6694179b8085703ee337a11","tid":1365880,"uid":287132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:22:12.000Z","msg":"打到深夜都要出，就係希望聽朝大家見到，真係關注下"},{"pid":"5f4a550af229b84c103ec1ccfe6f5127bdc109d4","tid":1365880,"uid":287132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:24:54.000Z","msg":"假消息唔係最難拆，最難拆係假消息當中撈一件真消息"},{"pid":"7851f30d096eaa63db03da28ad15bdf5e9333da5","tid":1365880,"uid":287132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:27:51.000Z","msg":"冷處理唔係最佳方法，拆依單嘢唔等於割蓆啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1686eb7412465c9063cb84db9bb55beb0fd7deca","tid":1365880,"uid":287132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:29:48.000Z","msg":"鄧重申，白衫人絕對不代表他們。對於「光復元朗」行動，他認為大家絕對有自由進行，但指真正為香港好的遊行人士，不會如此愚蠢，對圍村人士做出破壞行為，「我哋去遊行，係要林鄭撤回有五大訴求，千祈唔好自己都做咗啲違法行為。」他呼籲，村內的是村民私人財物，不論是不是古蹟，都不應該破壞，亦叮嚀大家在行動當日要「Be water」，「能進亦能退，唔好將自己變成一潭死水！」而他知悉警方不批出不反對通知書後，只表示十分無奈：「無言！」<br />\n<br />\n唔洗比click共媒01 ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/356386/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E5%85%A5%E6%9D%91%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E-%E5%B1%8F%E5%B1%B1%E5%8E%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E9%84%A7%E9%81%94%E6%99%BA-%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%88%91%E5%80%91?fbclid=IwAR1L9uuE943WxP2cNedUPf4rxX1MUwkg5_gk7uP1_GJSYon1a1d-yiBCr-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F356386%2F%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259D%2591%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E-%25E5%25B1%258F%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2584%25A7%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2599%25BA-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1L9uuE943WxP2cNedUPf4rxX1MUwkg5_gk7uP1_GJSYon1a1d-yiBCr-k&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=1c20bda0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/356386/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E5%85%A5%E6%9D%91%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E-%E5%B1%8F%E5%B1%B1%E5%8E%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E9%84%A7%E9%81%94%E6%99%BA-%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%88%91%E5%80%91?fbclid=IwAR1L9uuE943WxP2cNedUPf4rxX1MUwkg5_gk7uP1_GJSYon1a1d-yiBCr-k</a>"}]}